01:45.000 --> 01:51.009
connection with the Duke Marine Lab?

01:52.411 --> 01:55.395
Well, it'll be the same as it has with a number of 
other marine laboratories. They have an umbrella

01:55.495 --> 01:59.982
contract involving about five of us. 
bio-deterioration, studies on fouling

02:02.915 --> 02:16.559
organisms, boring organisms, physiology of 
