I want to return back to NSF in a second with the IDOE 
program. But before I move you away from ONR, I want

20:17.158 --> 20:24.790
to ask you a series of specific questions that are 
almost random. What is your connection with CG

20:25.190 --> 20:28.956
Bookout? He was my major professor. He and I have 
published together on 70 or 80 publications. He

20:39.427 --> 20:44.134
was the director of this laboratory before I 
became director. And he's a good friend. Is it his

20:47.479 --> 20:52.045
influence that turns you toward the study of 
crustacean lava?

