have a label of some sort. And a research associate 
in the term that is used there meant that I was not an

23:33.161 --> 23:40.248
appointed faculty member. I was working on soft 
money research grants for a long time. And during

23:45.714 --> 23:48.857
that period, I would have been labeled as a 
research associate. But you were still

23:49.017 --> 23:51.580
nevertheless working with crustaceans. Oh, yes. 
Okay. I was afraid for a while you were and a while

23:53.102 --> 23:55.464
you weren't. No, no. never really deviated from 
the crustacean realm. Okay, and crustacea,

24:00.219 --> 24:06.207
that's always been your interest as a marine 
biologist and oceanographer. Has your interest

24:06.227 --> 24:12.494
always centered primarily around coastal 
activity? Largely, although certain things have

24:12.514 --> 24:22.286
led me farther out into the ocean than others like 
this, the whole concept of distribution of

24:12.514 --> 24:22.286
larvae. Have you made any international voyages 
with other countries?

24:29.236 --> 24:30.277
