and supports research programs by American 
scientists dealing with systematics and ecology

26:04.243 --> 26:27.189
of terrestrial, freshwater, or estuarine marine 
animals and plants. But it has nothing to do with

26:28.370 --> 26:29.571
IDOE. But it never had any connection with IDOE? 
