26:33.655 --> 26:49.736
separate, discrete division of the National 
Science

26:33.655 --> 26:49.736
Foundation.

26:49.756 --> 26:53.821
Well, what exactly was your role in the 
Systematics of Ecology program? I've never had

26:53.841 --> 26:54.482
any. Never had any. I have you contacted with them 
for some reason. Heaven only knows why.

